Name: Average time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment across all process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Queued + Awaiting Assignment before transitioning to Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration of Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants that eventually include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Time from case start until Queued + Awaiting Assignment is first performed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Elapsed time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the subsequent occurrence of Completed + In Call within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants that do not contain Completed + In Call, compared to those that do
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call does not occur

Name: Total waiting time accumulated during Queued + Awaiting Assignment phases across all re-occurrences in a single case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Time between consecutive occurrences of Queued + Awaiting Assignment within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Cycle time of Queued + Awaiting Assignment defined as the time from its start to the start of the next activity in the variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Queued + Awaiting Assignment to Completed + Resolved in variants where Completed + In Call appears earlier in the sequence
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment when it directly precedes Accepted + Wait - User versus when it directly precedes Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Time elapsed from the first Queued + Awaiting Assignment to the final resolution (Completed + Closed) in cases containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of Queued + Awaiting Assignment when occurring after an initial Completed + In Call versus when occurring before any Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total time spent in Queued + Awaiting Assignment in high-performance variants (performance < 500,000) versus low-performance variants (performance > 1,000,000)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case
